# meme-generator

The meme-generator is a simple nodejs application running with docker an using imagemagick and following the tutorial from [@Erick Wendel](https://github.com/ErickWendel) below:

[Link for Tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MOpwfg1GJig&ab_channel=ErickWendel)

## Installation

Doesn't have nothing so easy like that! just have docker installed and run for the first time:

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

And some in other moment just use:

```bash
docker compose up
```

See ya! ðŸ‘‹